statements.sql: select * from `general_settings` limit 1
select * from `general_settings` limit 1
select * from `users` where `id` = 1 limit 1
select * from `general_settings` limit 1
select * from `users` where `id` = 1 limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1
select sum(`amount`) as aggregate from `deposits` where `status` = 1 and `user_id` = 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `support_tickets` where `user_id` = 1
select `remark`, `created_at`, SUM(amount) as Deposit from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `trx_type` = '+' and year(`created_at`) = '2025' group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%m'), `remark`
select `remark`, `created_at`, SUM(amount) as Payout from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `trx_type` = '-' and year(`created_at`) = '2025' group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%m'), `remark`
select `remark`, `created_at`, SUM(amount) as Airtime from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `remark` = 'airtime' and year(`created_at`) = '2025' group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%m'), `remark`

select `remark`, `created_at`, SUM(amount) as Internet from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `remark` = 'internet' and year(`created_at`) = '2025' group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%m'), `remark`
select `remark`, `created_at`, SUM(amount) as Cabletv from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `remark` = 'cabletv' and year(`created_at`) = '2025' group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%m'), `remark`
select `remark`, `created_at`, SUM(amount) as Utility from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `remark` = 'utility' and year(`created_at`) = '2025' group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%m'), `remark`

select `remark`, `created_at`, SUM(amount) as Insurance from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `remark` = 'insurance' and year(`created_at`) = '2025' group by DATE_FORMAT(created_at, '%m'), `remark`
select count(*) as aggregate from `users` where `ref_by` = 1
select `user_id`, sum(amount) as sums from `transactions` where year(`created_at`) = '2025' and `trx_type` = '+' group by `user_id` order by `amount` desc limit 5
select * from `users` where `users`.`id` in (5, 10, 14, 42, 174)
select `browser`, `os`, `country` from `user_logins` where `created_at` >= '2025-02-25 10:51:12'
select * from `user_logins` where `user_id` = 1 order by `id` desc limit 5 offset 1
select * from `user_logins` where `user_id` = 1 order by `id` desc limit 1
select * from `user_logins` where `user_id` = 1 order by `id` desc limit 1 offset 1
select * from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `trx_type` = '+' order by `id` desc limit 10
select * from `transactions` where `user_id` = 1 and `trx_type` = '-' order by `id` desc limit 10
select * from `support_tickets` where `user_id` = 1 and `status` = 1
select * from `frontends` where `data_keys` = 'seo.data' limit 1
select * from `extensions` where `act` = 'tawk-chat' and `status` = 1 limit 1
select * from `extensions` where `act` = 'google-analytics' and `status` = 1 limit 1
